1125static uint16_T look1_iu16lu64n48_binlcse(uint16_T u0, const uint16_T bp0[],



1126  const uint16_T table[], uint32_T maxIndex)



1127{



1128  uint16_T y;



1129  uint64_T frac;



1130  uint32_T iRght;



1131  uint32_T iLeft;



1132  uint32_T bpIdx;



1133



1134  /* Lookup 1-D



1135     Search method: 'binary'



1136     Use previous index: 'off'



1137     Interpolation method: 'Linear point-slope'



1138     Extrapolation method: 'Clip'



1139     Use last breakpoint for index at or above upper limit: 'off'



1140     Remove protection against out-of-range input in generated code: 'off'



1141     Rounding mode: 'simplest'



1142   */



1143  /* Prelookup - Index and Fraction



1144     Index Search method: 'binary'



1145     Extrapolation method: 'Clip'



1146     Use previous index: 'off'



1147     Use last breakpoint for index at or above upper limit: 'off'



1148     Remove protection against out-of-range input in generated code: 'off'



1149     Rounding mode: 'simplest'



1150   */



1151  if (u0 <= bp0[0U]) {



1152    iLeft = 0U;



1153    frac = 0ULL;



1154  } else if (u0 < bp0[maxIndex]) {



1155    /* Binary Search */



1156    bpIdx = maxIndex >> 1U;



1157    iLeft = 0U;



1158    iRght = maxIndex;



1159    while (iRght - iLeft > 1U) {



1160      if (u0 < bp0[bpIdx]) {



1161        iRght = bpIdx;



1162      } else {



1163        iLeft = bpIdx;



1164      }



1165



1166      bpIdx = (iRght + iLeft) >> 1U;



1167    }



1168



1169    frac = ((uint64_T)(uint16_T)((uint32_T)u0 - bp0[iLeft]) << 48) / (uint16_T)



1170      ((uint32_T)bp0[iLeft + 1U] - bp0[iLeft]);



1171  } else {



1172    iLeft = maxIndex - 1U;



1173    frac = 281474976710656ULL;



1174  }



1175



1176  /* Interpolation 1-D



1177     Interpolation method: 'Linear point-slope'



1178     Use last breakpoint for index at or above upper limit: 'off'



1179     Rounding mode: 'simplest'



1180     Overflow mode: 'wrapping'



1181   */



1182  if (table[iLeft + 1U] >= table[iLeft]) {



1183    y = (uint16_T)((uint32_T)(uint16_T)(((uint16_T)((uint32_T)table[iLeft + 1U]



1184      - table[iLeft]) * frac) >> 48) + table[iLeft]);



1185  } else {



1186    y = (uint16_T)((uint32_T)table[iLeft] - (uint16_T)(((uint16_T)((uint32_T)



1187      table[iLeft] - table[iLeft + 1U]) * frac) >> 48));



1188  }



1189



1190  return y;



1191}
